trans-unit.source: A class that enables you to associate easing functions with a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.QuaternionAnimationUsingKeyFrames"></xref> key frame animation.
trans-unit.target: En klassen som gjør det mulig å knytte gir enklere fungerer med en <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.QuaternionAnimationUsingKeyFrames"> </xref> nøkkel for animasjonen.

trans-unit.source: For an example of using an object similar to this one, see <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.EasingDoubleKeyFrame>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil se et eksempel ved bruk av et objekt som er lik denne en se <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.EasingDoubleKeyFrame>.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.EasingDoubleKeyFrame>

trans-unit.source: This class is used as part of a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.QuaternionKeyFrameCollection> in conjunction with a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.QuaternionAnimationUsingKeyFrames> to animate a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Quaternion> property value along a set of key frames.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen brukes som en del av en <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.QuaternionKeyFrameCollection>sammen med en <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.QuaternionAnimationUsingKeyFrames>å animere en <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Quaternion>egenskapsverdien langs et sett med nøkkelen for forhandleren.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Quaternion> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.QuaternionAnimationUsingKeyFrames> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.QuaternionKeyFrameCollection>

trans-unit.source: This <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.QuaternionKeyFrame> interpolates between the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Quaternion> value of the previous key frame and its own value linearly with an easing function to produce its output value.
trans-unit.target: Dette <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.QuaternionKeyFrame>interpolerer mellom den <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Quaternion>verdien for den forrige key rammen og sin egen verdi lineært med en easing funksjonen til å produsere utdata verdien.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Quaternion> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.QuaternionKeyFrame>
